title: Accupressure Guide
features: All the pressing point has been explained with the help of image for the ease of the user.
description: Acupressure technique is very ancient and very effective technique to cure many medical problems. Acupressure is an ancient healing art that uses the fingers to press key points on the surface of the skin to stimulate the body's natural self-curative abilities. When these points are pressed, they release muscular tension and promote the circulation of blood and the body's life force to aid healing.
